<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>검색결과: 없음</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: lightskyblue;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 300;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
        color: #222;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .container {
        width: 800px;
        background-color: #e7f5ff;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 25px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      .container button.go-home,
      .container button.go-report {
        background-color: #339af0;
        color: #fff;
        width: 200px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        border: none;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 18px;
        margin: 0 20px;
        outline: none;
      }
      .container button.go-report {
        background-color: #51cf66;
      }

      .container button.go-home:hover {
        background-color: #1864ab;
      }

      .container button.go-report:hover {
        background-color: #2b8a3e;
      }

      .container h1 {
        color: royalblue;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: normal;
        margin-bottom: 50px;
        font-size: 36px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      .container h3 {
        color: #4dabf7;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: normal;
        line-height: 2;
      }
      .button-box {
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 30px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>검색결과가 없습니다.</h1>
      <h3>
        다른 검색어를 입력해보세요. <br />
        누락된 정보가 있다면, '신규정보 등록하기'에서 직접 입력해주세요!
      </h3>
      <div class="button-box">
        <button class="go-home">
          <a href="/">홈 화면으로 이동</a>
        </button>
        <button class="go-report">
          <a href="./report">신규정보 등록하기</a>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
